thread.title_full: BRIEF-Mustek full-year headline EPS up 24.2 pct to 125.05 cents | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Mustek full-year headline EPS up 24.2 pct to 125.05 cents
text:
Sept 1 Mustek Ltd
* Fy revenue up 11.5 pct to r5.31 billion
* Fy mustek's headline earnings is 24.2 pct higher at 125.05 cents per share
* Fy dividend per share up 25.0 pct to 35.00 cents
* Fy net asset value per share up 11.7% to 959.00 cents Source text for Eikon:
